description:
This is a 19 minute workout called '15 MIN EXPRESS PILATES WORKOUT || At-Home Mat Pilates (Moderate)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Get ready to move with this Moderate Express Pilates Workout! This class can be suited to all levels so listen to your body and choose the modification that feels best for you.
